00:59:44.750 --> 00:59:48.620
in many cases been books that
would have been destroyed,

00:59:48.620 --> 00:59:52.940
certainly whole titles and many
times priceless manuscripts,

00:59:52.940 --> 00:59:55.580
they saved them in many cases.

00:59:55.580 --> 01:00:00.970
So we do have Nazis to thank for
that in a perverse kind of a way.

